"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T11:12:58.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"473befea3a6a9a6bc1617d007f25ed82def4ffd2","tid":1667198,"uid":93962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T11:16:05.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"7f14e9ff0622580a0381385be8efedbd8d690c7d","tid":1667198,"uid":108502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T11:47:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2822c89919046d89cdc7a0809f2451051ff45d85","tid":1667198,"uid":268123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T11:54:29.000Z","msg":"【香城施政報告2019】群策群力 轉危為機<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1656908\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1656908</a><br />\n<br />\n<em><strong>政治問題</strong></em><br />\n<br />\n- 重塑公民身分戶口政策保障國家、香港安全和利益<br />\n- 取消18區區議會、建立地域市政議會<br />\n- 禁止公務人員在任前、任內和任後獲港外榮典<br />\n- 改善高鐵一地兩檢操作方式<br />\n<br />\n<em><strong>便民基建</strong></em><br />\n<br />\n- 修正港鐵、巴士可加可減機制<br />\n- 完善機場集體運輸並加強機場、港珠澳大橋協同發展<br />\n- 興建東鐵、西鐵快速線並完善輕鐵和西鐵聯乘關係<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V1VCzpw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV1VCzpw.jpg&h=7b29ce56&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RYt8F4w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRYt8F4w.jpg&h=eecde813&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<em><strong>醫療、教育方向</strong></em><br />\n<br />\n- 以減少送院為目標的社區護理服務<br />\n- 重塑教育, 著重知識、技能層次分工<br />\n- 興建至少四所新區域全科醫院<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/B2D8F34.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FB2D8F34.png&h=cb82275f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n求正評及幫推！"},{"pid":"186195397c5462c5d5e624359726397d4e2b4ce2","tid":1667198,"uid":223491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T12:20:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"92bdd177cafc68a857dd4f38022b8eaca3a7e5dd","tid":1667198,"uid":289649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T12:24:14.000Z","msg":"[實用]    香城online防具升級詳細篇<br />\n<br />\n近呢一個月，我見到多左好多新入香城online嘅玩家，勇武/和理非都有好多工作做，鑑於有好多人唔知點配搭防具，眼見好多手足都只用貴價6092X，除左冇必要之外仲晒左好多錢，故此我係度再講一次點去配合適的防具。<br />\n<br />\n防毒面具：<br />\n中後/後防(物資站/噴漆師/文宣組/美化工程組/網上資訊組)<br />\n首選最合符經濟效益<br />\n包括單咀<br />\n3200/HF-52+3311K-55<br />\n一set最平100港幣有找<br />\n雙咀：<br />\n6200+6001/6003/6005(6005唔需要特登買，成本價貴)+5n11/5p71(唔建議5p71,如果要嘅不如買502再搭P100綿抵啲)+501蓋<br />\n例如：6200+6001CN+5n11+501 我見100已經有一set<br />\n而且 就算唔用5n11同501蓋 都ok 6001CN一對最平$30，我見$50通常都有<br />\n6003貴少少 $70成平價(睇你有冇運見到)<br />\n以上都可以頂到TG，但記得聞到味要即換<br />\n<br />\n想了解更多快啲入去連登睇啦😛<br />\n...<br />\n防毒面具篇完<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1666931\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1666931</a>"},{"pid":"54b550e125e74dee702270063afdea783de1826e","tid":1667198,"uid":231583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T12:25:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa9a558f4bc36266d1dbeedec4f8a1f3901b1bb2","tid":1667198,"uid":281020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T12:29:55.000Z","msg":"點解唔諗下整一本區議會議事規則出黎<br />\n當我地區議會過半就即刻修改"},{"pid":"edd12d71ee37360ede4f85974fb025c80f9054c7","tid":1667198,"uid":231583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T12:37:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7679285a2fa4b0932c50a49fb8b390730e8ba260","tid":1667198,"uid":231583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T12:40:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"531d3a8c4fcb0dae35d12ff3eba0869aa51ea613","tid":1667198,"uid":220045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T13:25:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ac07ae785d743be265880663e350bb85d6149cd2","tid":1667198,"uid":231583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T13:29:46.000Z","msg":"<